snippet.title: Quake Live - Official Steam Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Quake Live.

From the legendary series that founded the online shooter genre comes the most exciting, energetic, and fast-paced free-to-play shooter on the Internet. Play against players around the world in over 100 arenas, and a dozen game modes, in one of the most competitive shooters online today. 

Coming to Steam on September 17, 2014.

QUAKE LIVE™ © 2007-2014, Id Software LLC, a ZeniMax Media company. All Rights Reserved.

Music Credit:
R. Mullen
Performed by Yppah
Written by Jose Corrales Jr.
Published by Third Side Music o/b/o Just Isn't Music
Courtesy of Ninja Tune

ESRB RATING:TEEN with Language, Suggestive Themes, Violence
